INSERT INTO "public"."issue_comments" ("id", "company_id", "issue_id", "author_agent_id", "author_user_id", "body", "created_at", "updated_at") VALUES ($paperclip$8f9c7118-db0c-4f4f-ba3b-ca37e96e776d$paperclip$, $paperclip$712f694b-097f-4ca4-b161-f299187ec27d$paperclip$, $paperclip$4d0dbd31-02e8-4ed4-b9b5-122b1a362058$paperclip$, $paperclip$467192bf-0ffd-49de-b18f-91a35b60e57a$paperclip$, NULL, $paperclip$## Vault opnieuw aangemaakt

De vault folder bestond niet meer. Volledig opnieuw opgezet:

- `~/.paperclip/instances/default/vault/` aangemaakt met symlinks naar alle 5 agent workspaces (Nox, Mitch, Tommy, Oscar, Rex)
- `.obsidian/` config hersteld: Dataview, Templater, graph kleuren per agent
- `Home.md` met agent tabel en dashboard links
- 3 Dataview dashboards in `Dashboards/`
- 4 Templater templates in `_templates/`

### Vault openen

In Finder: **Cmd + Shift + G** → plak `~/.paperclip/instances/default/vault/`

In Obsidian: Open folder as vault → plak hetzelfde pad.

Daarna in Obsidian: Settings → Community Plugins → "Turn on" → Dataview en Templater activeren (config staat klaar, maar Obsidian moet de plugin code nog downloaden bij eerste keer).$paperclip$, $paperclip$2026-04-03T13:56:14.461Z$paperclip$, $paperclip$2026-04-03T13:56:14.461Z$paperclip$);
